		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>This robe is adorned with eyelike patterns. While you wear the robe, you gain the following benefits:</p></li><li><p><strong>All-Around Vision.</strong> The robe gives you Advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight.</p></li><li><p><strong>Special Senses.</strong> You have Darkvision and Truesight, both with a range of 120 feet.</p></li><li><p><em><strong>Drawbacks.</strong></em> A<em> </em><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.e4MmHYtpD4jFrRuH]{Light}</em> spell cast on the robe or a <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.jdFMmZrR5TJegYvD]{Daylight}</em> spell cast within 5 feet of the robe gives you the &amp;Reference[Blinded] condition for 1 minute. At the end of each of your turns, you make a Constitution saving throw (DC 11 for <em>Light</em> or DC 15 for <em>Daylight</em>), ending the condition on yourself on a success.</p></li></ul>",
